## 5.对称子串

### 题目描述

输入：abbaad，输出：abba

### 题解

```java
/**
 * @Author 歪鼻子
 * @Date 2020/10/13 13:49
 * @Description:
 * @Version 1.0
 */
public class Main {
    public static void findString(String s){
        /* 对字符串进行翻转 */
        String rever = new StringBuffer(s).reverse().toString();
        String res = "";
        int max = 0;
        int left = 0, right = 0;
        for (int i = 0; i < s.length(); i++){
            left = i;
            for ( right = s.length();;right--){
                if (left >= right) break;
                String ss = s.substring(left,right);
                /* tmp来存储当前的长度 */
                int tmp = right - left;
                /* 如果当前的长度大于之前的max，并且翻转的字符串包含了当前截取的字符串，那么截取的字符串就是对称了 */
                if (tmp > max && rever.contains(ss)){
                    res = ss;
                    max = tmp;
                }
            }
        }
        System.out.println(res);
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        String s = sc.nextLine();
        findString(s);
    }
}
```

