## 8.打印螺旋数组

### 题目描述

这道题在我校的OJ系统当中有，题目描述太难描述了，直接上网搜下吧，有这道理的相关描述

```java
/**
 * @Author 歪鼻子
 * @Date 2020/10/13 14:13
 * @Description:
 * @Version 1.0
 */
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        int row = 0, col = 0;
        Scanner sc = new Scanner(System.in);
        row = sc.nextInt();
        col = sc.nextInt();
        int a[][] = findSolution(row,col);
        for (int i = 0; i < row; i++){
            for (int  j = 0; j < col; j++){
                System.out.print(a[i][j]+" ");
            }
            System.out.println();
        }
    }

    /**
     * 核心思想其实比较好理解，我们定义一个top,bottom,left,right来记录画到一层了，例如我们将数组的第一行画好了，
     * 我们就需要将top进行++操作，如果最右边的连续数字画好了，我们就将right--，同理，bottom--，left++即可
     * 一个循环走完就是下一次循环
     */
    private static int[][] findSolution(int row,int col){
        int a[][] = new int [row][col];
        int top = 0, bottom = col-1;
        int left = 0, right = row-1;
        int i = top, j =left;
        int sum =1;
        while (true){

            /* 向右画图 */
            while ( j!= right+1){
                a[i][j] = sum;
                sum ++;
                j++;
            }
            /* 由于上一个循环的时候，j已经越界了，所以这里需要回弹一下（j是右边界） */
            j--;
            /* 这里为什么需要进行减一的原因主要是我们的sum++是在赋值之后再++的，所以最后一个位置的时候，sum必定是sum+1=row*col */
            if ((sum-1)==(row*col)){
                break;
            }
            /* 因为第一次while循环的时候，我们已经赋值了第一层了，所以top进行++ */
            top++;

            i = top;
            /* 向下画图 */
            while ( i != bottom+1 ){
                a[i][j] = sum;
                sum++;
                i++;
            }
            /* i这里也是由于越界了才退出上述循环，这里依旧还是回弹一下 */
            i--;
            if ((sum-1)==(row*col)){
                break;
            }
            /* 右一层已经赋值完成，再次往回缩一次 */
            right--;
            j = right;
            /* 从右向左画图了 */
            while ( j != left-1 ){
                a[i][j] = sum;
                sum++;
                j--;
            }
            j++;
            if ((sum-1)==(row*col)){
                break;
            }
            bottom--;
            i = bottom;
            /* 从下往上画图 */
            while ( i != top-1 ){
                a[i][j] = sum;
                sum++;
                i--;
            }
            i++;
            if ((sum-1)==(row*col)){
                break;
            }
            left++;
            j = left;
        }
        return a;
    }
}
```

## 9.代理模式

没啥输入输出要求，人工审题

```java
/**
 * @Author 歪鼻子
 * @Date 2020/10/13 18:03
 * @Description:
 * @Version 1.0
 */
interface Subject{
    void display();
}
class SiMaiTe implements Subject{

    @Override
    public void display() {
        System.out.println("产品展示");
    }
}
class SiMaiTeProxy implements Subject{
    private Subject proxy = null;
    @Override
    public void display() {
        proxy = new SiMaiTe();
        System.out.println("代理开始");
        proxy.display();
        System.out.println("代理结束");
    }
}
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        Subject proxy = new SiMaiTeProxy();
        proxy.display();
    }
}
```

## 10.抽象工厂

```java
/**
 * @Author 歪鼻子
 * @Date 2020/10/13 18:08
 * @Description:
 * @Version 1.0
 */
class Animal{
    private String name;

    public Animal(String name) {
        this.name = name;
    }
}
class Plant{
    private String name;

    public Plant(String name) {
        this.name = name;
    }
}
interface FarmFactory{
    Animal newAnimal();
    Plant newPlant();
}
class GuangZhouFactory implements FarmFactory{

    @Override
    public Animal newAnimal() {
        return new Animal("牛");
    }

    @Override
    public Plant newPlant() {
        return new Plant("蔬菜");
    }
}
class BeiJingFactory implements FarmFactory{

    @Override
    public Animal newAnimal() {
        return new Animal("马");
    }

    @Override
    public Plant newPlant() {
        return new Plant("水果");
    }
}
class FactoryProducer{
    public static FarmFactory getFactory(String choice){
        if (choice.equals("GUANGZHOU")){
            return new GuangZhouFactory();
        }else if (choice.equals("BEIJING")){
            return new BeiJingFactory();
        }
        return null;
    }
}
public class Main {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
        FarmFactory factoryA = FactoryProducer.getFactory("GUANGZHOU");
        Animal animalA = factoryA.newAnimal();
        Plant plantA = factoryA.newPlant();
        FarmFactory factoryB = FactoryProducer.getFactory("BEIJING");
        Animal animalB = factoryB.newAnimal();
        Plant plantB = factoryB.newPlant();
    }
}
```

# 使用GoLang实现一个简单的反向代理

## 1.创建两个服务

创建两个goroutine的服务分别监听的是8888端口跟9999端口，然后调用操作系统的信号量阻塞一下程序，让两个goroutine能够一直运行，作为一个GoLang Junior Developer最好是：Make English as your working language；所以程序当中我多数是采用英文进行注释。

创建一个web-main.go，执行一下以下代码吧

```go
type webHandlerFirst struct {

}
func(webHandlerFirst) ServeHTTP(writer http.ResponseWriter, request *http.Request)  {
	writer.Write([]byte("<h1>web-1</h1>"))
}
type webHandlerSecond struct {

}
func(webHandlerSecond) ServeHTTP(writer http.ResponseWriter,request *http.Request)  {
	// response string
	writer.Write([]byte("<h1>web-2</h1>"))
}
func main() {
	// this channel will blocking the main goroutine
	channel := make(chan os.Signal)
	// create goroutine to listening the port 8888
	go func() {
		http.ListenAndServe(":8888",webHandlerFirst{})
	}()
	// create goroutine to listening the port 9999
	go func() {
		http.ListenAndServe(":9999",webHandlerSecond{})
	}()
	// call system interrupt
	signal.Notify(channel,os.Interrupt)
	signal := <- channel
	// print signal signal log
	log.Println(signal)
}
```



